          />
          <p class="cs-item-p">
            I had J.R. Outdoor come help me on a job and my experience with him was awesome. 
            Very reasonably priced and did exactly what he said. Highly recommend doing business with J.R. Outdoor.
          </p>
          <span class="cs-reviewer">
